title: 'Saved By The Bell' star Lark Voorhies ends six-month marriage: report
text:
'Saved By The Bell' star Lark Voorhies rambles in bizarre interview 
Actress Lark Voorhies has filed for divorce just six months after exchanging vows with husband Jimmy Green in Las Vegas. 
The Saved By The Bell actress wed Green in April following a whirlwind courtship which began after the couple met on Facebook in 2014. 
In her divorce documents, obtained by TMZ.com , she's asking the court to cut any chances of spousal support for Jimmy. 
Meanwhile, he tells the news outlet his marriage to Voorhies has been a nightmare, insisting his mother-in-law was a big part of the couple's issues. Sponsored Links
